# ==============================================================================
# XVI. Deny Sensitive Environment Files
# ==============================================================================
# .envrc is permitted as the only sanctioned environment-configuration
# for Nix integration. All other .env* files are denied by default.
# .envrc.local is intentionally untracked — it holds maintainer-specific
# overrides (e.g. SDMX_MAIN_REMOTE=all) loaded via source_env_if_exists
# in .envrc and must never be committed.
.env*
!.envrc
.envrc.local

# ==============================================================================
# XVII. Transient Build and Runtime Artifacts
# ==============================================================================
# direnv state directory
/.direnv/
# Test coverage reports
/lcov.info
# Nix build symlinks
/result
/result-*

# ==============================================================================
# XVIII. Permanent Exclusions
# ==============================================================================
# Re-apply exclusions on top of allowed directories/files
# OS metadata
**/._*
**/.DS_Store
**/desktop.ini
**/Thumbs.db
# Editor & build artifacts
**/*.rs.bk
**/*.swp
**/*~
**/target/
